Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞少年 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有兩種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其一是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠對任何人下達命令並讓其絕對遵守的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其二是黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了毀滅他父皇統治的布里塔尼亞帝國而存在的 屬於他自己的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修以ZERO這個代號開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了替母后報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是為了創造妹妹娜娜莉能夠幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其行動究竟會孕育出何種結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在誰也不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 10
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}紅蓮 起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6}[主義者:對布里塔尼亞帝國現有政策不滿的布里塔尼亞人]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是間諜的話 真可謂堂而皇之啊 『主義者』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎 申請入團的人增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比預想的要簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然討厭布里塔尼亞  但不贊同恐怖手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是大多數ELEVEN的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說大部分ELEVEN支持黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托他們的福  大規模行動也變得容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,民眾不向政府通風報信就已經幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都的那個組織也說要提供給我們KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收到的情報也越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人很容易產生從眾心理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要創造出他們認可的標誌…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了這個 才假裝是『正義的使者』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不是都很喜歡嗎  『正義的使者』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那可不是『正義的使者』應該有的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是個被降了職的人呢 和你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 所以才想借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不打算就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就難說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到ZERO的線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,私立阿斯福德學院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能調查一下那裡的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,懷疑其中有ZERO的協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們因為軍務 不得不前往成田連山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這期間…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成田?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傳聞那邊不是日本解放戰線的大本營嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過於敏銳也令人頭疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是Glasgow吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫『無賴』 據說是由日本改造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手啊  黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入團的審查也不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說我們是精英 精英囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人熱血沸騰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都的人 連這東西都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是完全由日本製造的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮二式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有看過操作說明書了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,輻射波動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厲害的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 真令人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說京都的大人物也認同我們黑之騎士團了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的器材該怎麼用?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上過去 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒有辦法呢 新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城暫且不說 連井上他們也都飄飄然了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都好像同時支援著多個反抗組織呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終於也能夠晉身其中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你錯了 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這只不過是對我們的考驗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 也已經是非常了不起的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是樂觀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮二式 卡蓮 是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在人員也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就紅蓮的防禦力來說 你才應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也會乘坐無賴 不過戰鬥的王牌只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,況且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有著戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 打斷一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了一個奇怪的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是從希望入團的布里塔尼亞人那裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這會不會是想引出我們的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想探清內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是貿然和這個男人接觸又太過危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這情報又重要得讓人無法忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,週末去郊遊怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去成田連山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早飯哥哥的那份不需要準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要出門嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是從今天開始出去旅遊三天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近經常外出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是和戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第五區域  沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次定時聯絡在兩小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我們日本解放戰線的勢力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來談談話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們只需要無視一切異常狀況就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼急嘛 怎麼說也還是在執行軍務中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認ZERO傳來的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們向第二地點移動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO那傢伙 為什麼不用無賴的無線電…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 居然說是來郊遊 到底是想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是軍事訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有ZERO一個人在其他地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是想挖個溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為此才特意準備打樁機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒跟你提過什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  什麼也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO捨棄了所有會被反探知的通信設備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是來真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭 這一天終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以確定日本解放戰線的大本營在這個區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經把四個大隊分成七小隊埋伏在周圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只等總督一聲令下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣收攏包圍網將其殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有敵人在包圍網的外圍出現嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在作戰開始的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會將周圍道路以及所有山路全部封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有友軍在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果隨便現身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屆時將會是ZERO的末日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使說想要見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道對方是什麼人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方可是皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是庶民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼酒店挾持事件時的緣分 這算什麼緣分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我還沒向她道謝 向尤菲米婭殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是以前 這點小事我們家當然能辦到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為理事長的孫女到底有多大的社會地位啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…馬馬虎虎吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬馬虎虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說過要保護你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別一副監護人的嘴臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修 你為什麼是魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒空陪你研究哲學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家族的姓氏改成了『蘭佩魯基』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻保留了『魯魯修』這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為天真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法完全捨棄過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說的話 你的那個『C.C.』也太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像人類的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道雪為什麼是白色的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為已經忘記了自己曾經的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部人員就位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭按照預定 留在G-1進行後方支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救護班的指揮就由她負責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想說尤菲的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來不是應該讓她待在政廳的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的固執呢 這次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要親眼看看戰鬥的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個在那麼後方的部隊是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由ELEVEN作為駕駛員的友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎? 是Lancelot嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然讓NUMBERS來駕駛KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是絕不允許的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那支部隊是第二皇子殿下直接管轄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們根本無權干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 他們說想盡可能得到參加實戰的機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真的要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對手是柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其軍隊的強大 即使在布里塔尼亞也是屈指可數的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們還是和日本解放戰線合作…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不信任我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我拜託你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你來當我們的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督 時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 作戰開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被時代束縛的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘卻了自愛的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓你們隨同虛幻的夢想一起腐朽消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞軍已經把整座成田連山包圍起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其數量已經超過100了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開…開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照那個陣勢會被完全包圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連退路都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經被封鎖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在這裡展開戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥? 和布里塔尼亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和他們正面衝突嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被他們包圍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對手還是柯內莉婭的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前完全不同的大部隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們在這種情況下還能贏就是奇跡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 到現在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彌賽亞如果不創造奇跡也不會被認同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也需要奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇跡可不是那麼輕易降臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然讓你當首領還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,退路已經被斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有誰認為沒有我你們也能贏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向我開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然參加了黑之騎士團 那就只有兩條路可選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與我同生  或是  與我共死!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經被完全包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的地下協力者也全都被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,片瀨少將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭軍發來了勸降聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們在這裡屈服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那日本的抵抗運動就徹底完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 少將
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要主動出擊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是堅守城池?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂 籐堂在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了接收無賴·改而去了京都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四聖劍也和他同行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照預定 應該快回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無賴 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突破包圍網的一角 強行突圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上日本的尊嚴與志氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扭轉乾坤!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的大本營應該在山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但還未掌握正確的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是為了得到他們同黨的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能通過空襲把整座山直接炸毀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人應該會針對我軍包圍網的其中一點強行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁此機會推測其大本營的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我軍的正面戰力有三隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,達爾頓將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿歷克斯將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有柯內莉婭總督親自率領的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而側面戰力則有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人的ECM(電子干擾裝置)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方部隊應該馬上就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我方也開啟ECCM(電子反干擾裝置)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將通訊頻道調到α-4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的…  叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是說『無賴』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 只有那種Glasgow模仿機需要小心應付
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦? 將這座山要塞化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下 請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我和那些普通女人相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是大將的首級!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無禮之徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們轉為掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 柯內莉婭在此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有敢來殺我的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來挑戰我啊 把我殺了試試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切 隨你高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你是首領呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深表感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地區已發出避難命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還有未撤離的人 請迅速撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重複 這個地區已發出避難命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼選擇這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Code-R的實驗資料如果被軍方發現就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來以為設在恐怖份子的勢力範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,軍方不容易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,決定這事的是巴托雷將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在說這個也無濟於事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方火力正向這裡集中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定找到大本營所在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二輪攻擊也不奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有如此可怕的鎮壓力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,達爾頓將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從敵人行動目的的分析結果來看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線的大本營入口估計是在那個山莊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況 應該說Bingo嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 正確來講…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,配合我一下嘛  你這個老實人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是… 達爾頓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的大本營在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們就在此待機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒有搶奪部下功勞的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓預備部隊趕到達爾頓那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,達爾頓的勳章又要增加了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,極為合理的佈陣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是越是精湛的佈陣反而越容易解讀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連你的位置也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,預備部隊不是要趕到達爾頓將軍那裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我隊被命令要在柯內莉婭總督的後方待機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也叫後方?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主戰場的外圍的外圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方讓我如何洗刷污名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中村隊 通信中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三區域 沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉田少校 戰死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑田和倉田也被擊敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永井怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果籐堂在的話 神風便會再次捲起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能再一次創造『嚴島的奇跡』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會太強硬了 籐堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈 千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備無賴·改
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也告訴後面的浦部和仙波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通向成田的道路全部被封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能趕得及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來AREA-11的反政府勢力就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 所有準備都已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之騎士團 全員出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 只有硬上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就來創造一次奇跡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始我們黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從山頂向布里塔尼亞軍發動奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽從我的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向著第三地點一口氣衝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,俘獲布里塔尼亞第二皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,負責突擊殺開血路的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮二式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 使用三號貫通電極
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一擊定乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出力確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,輻射波動啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外載狀態維持
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外輸傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 這麼大規模的山崩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿歷克斯隊和達爾頓隊會全滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利用鉤索移動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下請退後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿歷克斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快調查達爾頓的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡能撐住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是中心部位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦啦 這樣下去會一直衝到山腳下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熱能反應異常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會有誰故意引發了水蒸氣爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若不用上拉庫夏塔的輻射波動的話是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們沒有關係 你就這麼保持待機就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎預想的破壞力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然成功孤立了柯內莉婭隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是需要更慎密一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,物理老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也包括概率的問題 還是請教一下妮娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山頂方向確認出現新的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡硫斯隊已經前去迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 想要趁亂攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡硫斯隊緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是日本解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼? 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能隨便離開自己的崗位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是非常事態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要飛黃騰達的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟著我上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭的援軍有限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作氣突破!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此就大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的任務是掩護ZERO的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡硫斯隊全滅?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須在ZERO接觸柯內莉婭殿下之前做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,維蕾塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背水之陣加上懸崖俯衝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到古典的戰法居然如此有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話就和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞·哥特瓦爾德決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦? 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還待在軍隊裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我現在可沒時間陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ORANGE君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,O…O… 居然還敢提ORANGE!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是初次見到的KnightMare機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,區區ELEVEN怎麼可能會有那樣的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是這傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這傢伙把卡硫斯的部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看見了嗎? 布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於… 終於可以和你們對等戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這台紅蓮二式正是我們反擊的  開始!
